# Custom TTP Template Index
#
# This file registers custom TTP templates for auto-discovery.
# Format: Template, Hostname, Platform, Command
#
# - Template: Filename of template (in this directory)
# - Hostname: Regex to match device hostname (use .* for all)
# - Platform: Device platform (e.g., cisco_ios, arista_eos)
# - Command: Regex to match command
#
# Unlike TextFSM, TTP has no built-in templates, so this index is the only
# way to enable auto-discovery for TTP parsing.
#
# Example entries (uncomment to use):
# custom_show_interfaces.ttp, .*, cisco_ios, show interfaces
# datacenter_bgp.ttp, dc-.*, cisco_ios, show ip bgp.*
# special_version.ttp, router-[0-9]+, cisco_ios, show version

Template, Hostname, Platform, Command
custom_show_interfaces.ttp, .*, cisco_ios, show interfaces
